'''载体蛋白'''（{{lang-en|carrier protein}}）简称“'''载体'''”，又称'''转运体'''（{{lang-en|transporter}}），是参与[[离子|离子]]、小[[分子|分子]]或[[高分子|高分子]]跨越[[生物膜|生物膜]]进行运输的一类多回旋折叠[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]。<ref>{{cite book
 |author       = Sadava, David, et al.
 |title        = Life, the Science of Biology
 |edition      = 9th
 |publisher    = Macmillan Publishers
 |year         = 2009
 |ISBN         = 1429219629
 |page         = 119
 |url          = http://ebooks.bfwpub.com/life9e.php
 |language     = en
 |access-date  = 2011-10-02
 |archive-date = 2011-09-19
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20110919165719/http://ebooks.bfwpub.com/life9e.php
 |dead-url     = yes
}}</ref>载体蛋白都是[[跨膜蛋白|跨膜蛋白]]，它们能在[[协助扩散|协助扩散]]或[[主动运输|主动运输]]过程中将被运载物从自身所处的膜的一端转运到另一端，有载体蛋白参与的物质转运机制被统称为[[载体介导转运|载体介导转运]]。<ref>{{cite book
 |author      = Thompson, Liz A.
 |title       = Passing the North Carolina End of Course Test for Biology
 |publisher   = American Book Company, Inc.
 |year        = 2007
 |ISBN        = 1598071394
 |page        = 97
 |url         = http://www.americanbookcompany.com/newsite/samplebooks/SAMPLE%20PAGES%20-%20Passing%20the%20North%20Carolina%20End%20of%20Course%20Test%20in%20Biology/#/1/
 |language    = en
 |deadurl     = yes
